Text: The Music Alarm Clock is an alarm clock that plays your favorite tunes when you want! Just list your music and schedule the time to start your list to be played. You can use music from your computer or directly from the CD. For those who have the habit of sleeping with the PC on, this is the best option to wake up in a good mood! Additional Information: Version: 3.2 Compression:. Rar Language: English Runs on Windows 98, XP, Vista and 7 Size: 730 Kb
